import React, { useContext } from 'react';
import Switch from 'react-switch';
import { ThemeContext } from 'styled-components';

import { ContainerContact, TextTitle, SubTextTitle, SubContainerContact, BoxContact, Icon, BoxTexts, TitleContact, LinkText } from './styles';
import { FiArrowDown } from "react-icons/fi";
interface Props {
    toggleTheme(): void;
}

const Contact: React.FC<Props> = ({ toggleTheme }) => {
    const { colors, title } = useContext(ThemeContext);

    return (
        <ContainerContact>
            <TextTitle>Contato</TextTitle>
            <SubTextTitle>Caso você queira entrar em contato sinta-se à vontade usando um dos links abaixo</SubTextTitle>

            <SubContainerContact>
                <BoxContact>
                    <Icon></Icon>

                    <BoxTexts>
                        <TitleContact>Linkedin</TitleContact>
                        <LinkText></LinkText>
                    </BoxTexts>
                </BoxContact>

                <BoxContact>
                    <Icon></Icon>

                    <BoxTexts>
                        <TitleContact>Linkedin</TitleContact>
                        <LinkText></LinkText>
                    </BoxTexts>
                </BoxContact>

                <BoxContact>
                    <Icon></Icon>

                    <BoxTexts>
                        <TitleContact>Linkedin</TitleContact>
                        <LinkText></LinkText>
                    </BoxTexts>
                </BoxContact>

                <BoxContact>
                    <Icon></Icon>

                    <BoxTexts>
                        <TitleContact>Linkedin</TitleContact>
                        <LinkText></LinkText>
                    </BoxTexts>
                </BoxContact>
                <BoxContact>
                    <Icon></Icon>

                    <BoxTexts>
                        <TitleContact>Linkedin</TitleContact>
                        <LinkText></LinkText>
                    </BoxTexts>
                </BoxContact>


            </SubContainerContact>
        </ContainerContact>
    );
}

export default Contact;
